title: S15 Ep97: Born Haunted w/ Nate Michael
itunes:title: Born Haunted w/ Nate Michael
description:
Darkness Radio find out what it is like to be Born Haunted with guest Nate Michael

Have you ever wondered what it's like to live in a real haunted house? Growing up with a ghost? What if nearly every home you lived in had unexplained phenomena? Would you think that it's you; that you were born haunted?

Today, real life experiencer, Nate Michael details his horrifying occurrences with the strange & supernatural in these gripping & terrifying real life encounters. From demons in the closet, to the lost souls of those once murdered; join Dave & Tim and witness the true stories of growing up haunted.
